{"tid":1407133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（置頂）（致poly學生會）你地既ocamp可以放心搞 因為你地需要既係放鬆","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:57:22.000Z","uid":71807,"like":49,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de5025fc7624a26498696be32691c93439b971ed","tid":1407133,"uid":71807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"Poly學生會有冇幫手，大家有發夢既都見到 詳細我唔多講，唔明點解會有人開post屌佢地，仲要咁多個like。不分化、不分割，但每次都係由連登仔屌人先。發夢壓力大，適當既放鬆係絕對需要，我唔想再見到有人出事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更何況去既人可能每次發夢都有出，點解要標籤佢地？每個人既青春係屬於自己，我唔希望見到佢地18歲入學既青春只係得發夢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地已經好努力，就由我地班廿幾歲既老屎忽出黎頂埋你地個份！放心去玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我係到有個建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地不如dem返個 beat屬於香港人既beat，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命！自由無罪</span></span><br />\n玩一個屬於香港人既game 有口罩頭盔寫字貼身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，我愛你地</span></span>"},{"pid":"09aad2a174cd2eadc8bc117e4de8339f94270b68","tid":1407133,"uid":71807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af006f03bdc511de40e9be48f63fef45839ddbe4","tid":1407133,"uid":73200,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c524b796dab8ff75c1fc98ad5ba3e88c09fc776f","tid":1407133,"uid":71807,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"af006f03bdc511de40e9be48f63fef45839ddbe4","tid":1407133,"uid":73200,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"我只係現場發夢既人 我諗你應該冇落過現場 唔知佢地冒住咩風險幫我地"},{"pid":"88440b52e537daacdc65f2b18e630d78ef92b305","tid":1407133,"uid":242615,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,